Name: Co-Ba122
Sentence: Although T c,onset of 2 mol.% BZO-Co-Ba122 thin film values are 24.6 K, which is slightly lower than that of 0 mol.% Co-Ba122 thin film, its value is higher than that of bulk samples (T c = 22 K) [34] and it is similar to that of Co-Ba122 thin film on oxide substrates .

Name: Co-Ba122
Sentence: A sharp superconducting transition temper- ature (T c ) at 27.1 K (T c,onset ) with a narrow transition width ( where T c 90 and T c 10 are defined as 90% and 10% of the resistivity, respectively) of 1.0 K was observed in the 0 mol.% BZO-Co-Ba122 thin film on CaF 2 substrate, which is comparable with the previously reported highest T c and narrowest ÎT c for Co-Ba122 thin films [13].
